<!--StartFragment-->

\-------Lyrics---------------- 

**NOTHING WILL STOP ME** 

**Verse** 

Putting on the Garment of Praise for the Spirit of heaviness.

 Basking in your Glory, the oil of Joy overflowing.

 I give you the praise you deserve Lord.

 Your presence I love and I life. For eternity, I will praise you for all my days.

 **CHORUS**

 Nothing Will Stop me from Shouting, 

Singing, praising you my God

 Because you are Bigger, Stronger, greater,

 Awesome are you Lord 

**Verse**

 Jesus you mean more than life to me and for ever I will shout your fame

 Every other creature wished 

They had words to express your greatness just like I do 

Itâ€™s a privilege for me to lift my hands, with your words in my mouth 

I will praise you for all my days 

**Chorus 2x**

 Nothing Will Stop me from Shouting,

 Singing, praising you my God Because you are Bigger, Stronger, greater, 

Awesome are you Lord

 **Bridge 2x** 

Oh oh you are bigger, you are stronger

 Oh oh I give you all my praise, receive all my praise

 **Chorus** 

Nothing Will Stop me from Shouting,

 Singing, praising you my God Because you are Bigger, Stronger, greater, 

Awesome are you Lord End 

Because the greater lives inside of me 

Nothing can steal my praise 

My Praise is my Joy It is my victory 

Hallelujah

Watch Lyric video **[HERE](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IucTt31toIc&feature=youtu.be)**

summary: With a subtle and melodious voice, Karine takes the audience into a deep realm of worship.  When you step into a place of worship, this song keeps you on your knees. For everything God has done in your life, what can stop your praise?
